            "summary": "Perbaiki Salin Reset",
            "content_html": "<div><div style=\"margin: 1rem 0; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <textarea id=\"inputText\" rows=\"6\" style=\"width:100%; margin-bottom: 1rem;\" placeholder=\"Tulis teks di sini...\"></textarea>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\">\n    <button onclick=\"fixText()\">Perbaiki</button>\n    <button onclick=\"copyText()\">Salin</button>\n    <button onclick=\"resetText()\">Reset</button>\n  </div>\n\n  <textarea id=\"outputText\" rows=\"6\" style=\"width:100%;\" readonly placeholder=\"Hasil perbaikan akan muncul di sini...\"></textarea>\n</div>\n</div>",
